<h2>Calculate In Real Time</h2>

<h3>Given interest portion, calculate interest rate earned over a given period</h3>

<%= form_for :compute_interest_rate,   url:real_time_tvom_results_path do |f| %>
Interest earned in dollars: <%= f.number_field :interest_portion %> <br>
present value: <%= f.number_field :pv %> <br>
time in days: <%= f.number_field :time %>
<%= f.submit "Compute interest rate" %>
<% end %>
<br>
<br>

<h3>Given interest rate and future value, calculate size of annuity payment needed to accumulate that future sum </h3>

<%= form_for :compute_annuity_payment, url:real_time_tvom_results_path do |f| %>
Interest Rate: <%= f.number_field :interest_rate %> <br>
Compounding Frequency: <%= f.number_field :compounding_frequency %><br>
Compounding Periods: <%= f.number_field :compounding_periods %><br>
Future Value: <%= f.number_field :fv %>
<%= f.submit "Compute interest rate" %>
<% end %>
